      "content": "thanks. i'm a bit nervous about the electrical side of things though. since it's making that weird buzzing noise even when it's not spinning, is there any way the electricity could just be acting up or jumping around unexpectedly? like is there any chance of a short circuit that doesn't look obvious?",
